# SOC Wazuh Homelab

## Overview

This project demonstrates the deployment of a Security Operations Center (SOC) using Wazuh to monitor Linux systems, detect attacks, investigate alerts and document incident response.

## Technologies

- Ubuntu Server
- Kali Linux
- Wazuh
- Linux Audit
- File Integrity Monitoring
- MITRE ATT&CK

```mermaid
flowchart LR

    A["💻 Windows 11 Host"]

    subgraph VirtualBox
        B["🖥️ Ubuntu Server<br/>Wazuh Manager<br/>Wazuh Indexer<br/>Wazuh Dashboard"]
        C["⚔️ Kali Linux"]
    end

    C -->|"SSH / Nmap / Attacks"| B
    B -->|"Alerts & Logs"| A
    A -->|"HTTPS :5601"| B
```
